chunks.cleaned_english_translation: On the story of a lame woman from the city of Mainz. She came to the festival of Blessed Goar. Placed before Abbot Tancred, she was healed while the clergy completed the evening psalms.
chunks.original_latin:
De muliere clauda ex urbe Mogontiaco. 24. Ex urbe Mogontiaco ad festivitatem B. Goaris
mulier clauda posito coram abbate Tancrado venit,
et cum in vigiliarum de vespertini psalmi a clero
complerentur, sanata est.
